==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: coupled
<hw>coupled</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>joined together
especially in a pair or pairs.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> conjugate, conjugated.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>connected by a physical link, as railway cars or
trailer trucks. Opposite of <ant>unconnected</ant> or
<ant>unlinked</ant></def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> joined, linked.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Couplement</ent>⟦br⟧
